Package: multimix
Title: Biphasic Temporal Decomposition Logistic Mixed Effects Model
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Date: 2026-03-23
Authors@R:
    person("Michelle", "Fang", , "fangm@ccf.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1548-010X"))
Description: Fits and visualizes biphasic temporal decomposition logistic mixed
    effects models for longitudinal binary outcomes. The model decomposes
    temporal patterns into early and late phases with subject-specific random
    effects, using Gauss-Hermite quadrature for numerical integration and
    L-BFGS-B optimization. Includes both a full model with two random effects
    and a lite variant with a single shared random effect.
